name: Abhishek Kumar
message: ​Ritesh Agarwal, the founder and CEO of OYO Rooms, has an estimated net worth of approximately ₹16,000 crore, which is equivalent to around $2 billion USD. This places him among the world's billionaires; however, he does not rank within the top 200 on Forbes' 2025 World's Billionaires list, where the 200th position is held by individuals with significantly higher net worths. In India, Agarwal is among the youngest billionaires, but he is not listed among the top 10 richest Indian billionaires, whose net worths are substantially higher.
